Jackson, from Kenya
Carlito, from Argentina
Zahira, from Morocco
Samuel, from India...
four children who live very far away from each other and who have never met but who have a common point: they have to cover tremendously long distances to reach their school. 
On foot, on horseback or in a wheelchair, but all with an extraordinary determination...
